-672444635.text: "In SUM149, the levels of total FAK1 in treated cells were similar to the control during the first 72h of treatment, decreasing from 0.4-0.2 ng total FAK1 and mug protein after 96-120h of CEP-37440 treatment; however there was a slightly decrease of phospho-FAK1, decreasing from 0.019 Units phospho-FAK1 and mug protein in the control to 0.008-0.009 Units phospho-FAK1 and mug protein at 96-120 h of CEP-37440 treatment."
